import { React, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; const PartnerDashboard = () => { const { restaurant, restaurants } = useSelector(state => ({ ...state })); const [restaurantDet, setRestaurantDet] = useState(''); useEffect(() => { if(!restaurant) { } }, [restaurant, restaurants]) return (

{restaurant?.restaurantName}

{restaurant?.contact}
{restaurant?.email}
{restaurant?.restaurantAddress}, {restaurant?.city}, {restaurant?.state}, {restaurant?.zipCode}
{restaurant?.status}

Owner Details

{restaurant?.firstName}
{restaurant?.lastName}
{restaurant?.establishmentType}
{ restaurant?.outletType.map(outlet => outlet.toLowerCase())?.join(', ') }
{ restaurant?.cuisinesType.map(cuisine => cuisine.toLowerCase())?.join(', ') }
) } export default PartnerDashboard;
